title: Blue Jays beat Rangers 6-3 to win wild Game 5
text:
> Texas Blue Jays beat Rangers 6-3 to win wild Game 5 Toronto Blue Jays shortstop Troy Tuloqwitzki talks with the umpires after a call during the seventh inning in Game 5 of baseball's American League Division Series against the Texas Rangers, Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015 in Toronto. (Nathan Denette/The Canadian Press via AP) MANDATORY CREDIT
